query:
WITH entities AS (
            SELECT c.id FROM core_collaterals c
            INNER JOIN core_collateral_events ce ON c.id = ce.id
            WHERE ce.event_type = 'initialized'
              AND (ce.event ->> 'credit_facility_id')::UUID = $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, CASE WHEN $2 THEN e.context ELSE NULL::jsonb END as "context: es_entity::ContextData", e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_collateral_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.id, e.sequence
